00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:57,860
Toto je pre teba.

263
00:19:58,540 --> 00:19:59,660
Ako sa voláš?

264
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:00,900
Chen Xiao.

265
00:20:01,600 --> 00:20:03,760
Aj moje priezvisko je Chen.

