00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:07,120
Malá sestra, prijímam ťa.

268
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:09,340
Počúvajte,

269
00:20:10,080 --> 00:20:11,160
odo dnes,

270
00:20:11,600 --> 00:20:14,240
Chen Xiao, bude adoptívna sestrička Chen You You.

271
00:20:14,900 --> 00:20:16,420
