437
00:30:28,800 --> 00:30:30,140
Pane, váš telefón.

438
00:30:35,300 --> 00:30:36,000
Haló?

439
00:30:36,540 --> 00:30:38,140
Haló, dedko?

440
00:30:38,380 --> 00:30:39,660
To si ty, Qing Qing?

